bert Buckland",,"2015-03-25T14:40:33.367Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/227686/answer","Biography information for Robert Buckland","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/227686/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/227686/answer",,,,,"88","Attorney General","Attorney General","2015-03-17","Staff","1","House of Commons","To ask the Attorney General, how many and what proportion of employees in the Law Officers Departments identify as (a) white or white British, (b) Asian or Asian British, (c) Black or Black British, (d) mixed or multiple ethnic group and (e) another ethnicity.","false","Biography information for Gloria De Piero","Ashfield","Gloria De Piero","227952"
